Dialogue: 10,0:00:03.07,0:00:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t hold it anymore...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.55,0:00:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm losing my mind...} I'm out of my mind...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.91,0:00:20.68,Thought,,0,0,0,,D-Damn...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.68,0:00:24.86,Thought,,0,0,0,,I'd heard rumors, but to think this kind of stuff \Nreally {secretly }happens in the girls' section of the school...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.87,0:00:33.81,Thought,,0,0,0,,Is this for real?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.10,0:00:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?! {?????? maybe nani, maybe the girl's name}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.13,0:00:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A boy! A boy's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.95,0:00:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{untranslated line? sounds like "iie"}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.34,0:01:04.81,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Oh crap... {mazui?}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.76,0:01:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.76,0:01:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A boy snuck into the school!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:10.53,0:01:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.39,0:01:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.33,0:01:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That klutz!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:17.10,0:01:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!\NWasn't that Kuroiwa from Class 2-G?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.20,0:01:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This'll get him expelled for sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.69,0:01:28.04,Thought,,0,0,0,,Good thing it wasn’t Yuji-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.21,0:01:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A new laxative? {(bowel) movement; evacuation; defecation}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.32,0:01:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You dummy! It’s the pill.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:44.42,0:01:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The pill? You mean {\i1}that{\i0} kind of...? {lit: is it that day's}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.59,0:01:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. You never know when\Nyou’ll end up making love, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.94,0:01:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's up to the girl to\Ntake that kind of precaution. {https://jisho.org/search/tashinami}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.06,0:01:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Manami-san, is the pill salty or sweet?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.57,0:01:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, you...!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.18,0:02:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The pill isn’t candy!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.18,0:02:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But I kinda wanna taste one... just to know.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.62,0:02:05.67,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Look here...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.11,0:02:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The pill only works if you take it every day!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.36,0:02:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That’s such a hassle. {inconvenient}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.86,0:02:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness! This is why\NI can’t deal with late bloomers!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.86,0:02:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you’re not having sex, you don’t need it!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.29,0:02:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s kinda boring.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.86,0:02:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t mope, my friend.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.08,0:02:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Infiltrating the girls’ part is practically tradition
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.37,0:02:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,for us in Jouka Academy's boys' department! {traditional ritual}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.85,0:02:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it pisses me off, Yuji!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.32,0:02:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally got that perfect focus shot! {gutchon no focus from the ep title}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.68,0:02:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! You guys never learn!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.85,0:02:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Whassat?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.08,0:02:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori! Let's get this straight. You girls get all excited 'cause we’re barred from your building,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.38,0:02:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and do all sorts of risque stuff in secret, \Nso of course it fires up our craving to sneak in! {lit: dangerous things}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.26,0:02:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What risque stuff?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.68,0:02:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I know all about it!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.83,0:02:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You girls grope each other \Nand twist it around and stuff, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.23,0:03:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Lesbians. Total lesbians.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.01,0:03:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s that vulgar pinky for?! {referring to him sticking out a pinky to hint at something lewd}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.23,0:03:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, maybe some of the girls, \Nbut we definitely don’t do that kind of stuff!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.81,0:03:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.02,0:03:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.28,0:03:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.23,0:03:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, you two have gotten so close! {sekkin - becoming close (i.e. friendly); becoming intimate}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.71,0:03:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you stop making a show of it? {your friendship" probably}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.67,0:03:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We weren't trying to!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.72,0:03:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If you two get too chummy, \Nit’s irritating!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.03,0:03:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re not!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.09,0:03:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.85,0:03:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Like I’d ever get all buddy-buddy with Saori!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.18,0:03:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, knock it off with the borderline criminal infiltration games. It’s for your own good!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.98,0:03:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true. \NAll of you’ll get exposed for it sooner or later.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.07,0:03:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, the boys’ side \Nwill be drowning in suspensions.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.55,0:03:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a little suspension \Ncan scare a man from Jouka!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.33,0:03:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s all about how you do it. \NI’ll prove it to you within a week.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.82,0:03:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.90,0:03:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You three, especially Saori,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.34,0:03:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,go wash your necks... no, wait—\Nbetter wash your underwear real good! {kubi aratte - washing one's neck is some expression of treat in japanese}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.55,0:03:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And be extra careful when you change!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.23,0:04:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What the...?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.86,0:04:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, the enemy's not messing around either.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.89,0:04:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This just stokes the fire \Nof my craving to sneak in.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.82,0:04:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Another troublemaker from Class 2-G?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.25,0:04:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuike-sensei!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.47,0:04:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you explain \Nyour homeroom class’s behavior?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.14,0:04:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice Principal!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.33,0:04:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Akimoto-sensei?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.60,0:04:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though this is a co-ed school, \Nthe girls’ and boys’ buildings are walled off!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.59,0:04:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s practically railroading any two kids \Nwho love each other to jump straight to sex! {?? not sure she means this}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.59,0:04:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What are you implying?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.10,0:04:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just asking you to be lenient \Nwith Kuroiwa-kun this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.31,0:04:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.89,0:04:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no need to even \Nbother the Director with this! {??? idk what he means: there won't be even asking director for his opinion/instructions - no idea why he brings up the director at all}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.04,0:04:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Our rules are ironclad, airtight, and absolute! {ironclad, iron plate, and *something else about iron*} {imatu: "ironfisted"? "ironhanded"?}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.43,0:05:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, Akimoto-sensei, your courage \Namazes me every time.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.95,0:05:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It really should’ve been me, \Nas their homeroom teacher, saying that.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.44,0:05:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It is our duty as teachers in our twenties \Nto protect those kids
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.77,0:05:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,from the decrepit old customs of this school.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.80,0:05:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s keep supporting each other, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.50,0:05:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.61,0:05:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.18,0:05:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, it’s spreading.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.12,0:05:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, your fly is undone.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.13,0:05:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuike-sensei, when you’re flustered, it only digs in deeper. Don’t move. I’ll free it for you. {/undo}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.12,0:05:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My, someone’s full of life today.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.40,0:05:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So... I’m sure you all already know \Nabout yesterday’s incident.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.42,0:06:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And the girls’ side \Nisn’t entirely blameless either.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.81,0:06:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, sir?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.98,0:06:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm saying is, \Ndon’t give the boys any weird ideas.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.33,0:06:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Act like proper, modest high school students. \NThat's what I want you to be mindful of...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.83,0:06:17.54,Thought,,0,0,0,,Fukuike-sensei is oddly refreshed today...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.54,0:06:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.09,0:06:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It definitely feels like \Nhe just beat off somewhere. {jerked off/came one shot}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.88,0:06:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.85,0:06:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what do you mean\Nby "beat off," Manami-san? {very vulgar and unmistakably obscene wording}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.30,0:06:27.63,Top,,0,0,0,,Y-Yuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.63,0:06:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Kobayashi! \NDon’t say stuff like that in class!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.44,0:06:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But Saori and Manami were just...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.63,0:06:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that kind of explicit talk and behavior \Nthat arouses the curiosity of the boys! {itazura - to fool around with, also means lewd behavior; rokotsu - unconcealed/blatant/plain but can also mean lewd/indecent}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.32,0:06:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! I've never aroused anyone yet! {itazura}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.01,0:06:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And when they say "boner," \Nwhat kind of bone is that? {??? idk, kaku can mean everything and the kitchen sink}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.63,0:06:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,When they say "it stands up," what is "it"? {literal}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.79,0:06:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Seriously, you don't understand at all?! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.77,0:06:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So explicit is like... this? {again, not sure which of the meanings of rokotsu this is}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.28,0:06:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, you snapped! {puttsun}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.81,0:07:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? If that’s explicit, \Nthen this is explicit too, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.74,0:07:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Like that! {??? sore?}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.37,0:07:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Make it stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.17,0:07:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s nothing. \NReal explicit stuff is more like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.51,0:07:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Study on your own\Nfor the remainder of class today! {studying by oneself (at school) while the teacher is absent​}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.01,0:07:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.52,0:07:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And thus, we've secured an early dismissal.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.34,0:07:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We really did! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.27,0:07:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Who goes there?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.07,0:07:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yikes... No way we’ll ever get \Nto the other side at this rate. {????????? are ja **** tottemo muri}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.87,0:07:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear, Sakazaki?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.56,0:07:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you’re a genius at special makeup, \Nyou’re not gonna fly over there like some fly-man.{hae otoko - literally "fly (the insect) man"}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.57,0:07:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.08,0:07:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot. Why would I ever try \Nsomething that conspicuous?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.92,0:08:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't screw this up, Sakazaki. \NWe’re really counting on your heroics here. {brilliant achievement; spectacular feat; splendid accomplishment; remarkable deed}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.34,0:08:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.55,0:08:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, aside from hopping over the fence,\Nthe only other route is that one connector path.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.29,0:08:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.94,0:08:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I’m back.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.75,0:08:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The girls’ classes sure are exhausting.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.53,0:08:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.21,0:08:37.16,Thought,,0,0,0,,Wow! Our school's girls are second to none! {??????????? onna no **** **** ***}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.71,0:08:44.48,Thought,,0,0,0,,That was a close call... {abunai?}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.81,0:08:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Infiltration successful!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.27,0:08:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All righty, then...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.92,0:09:11.81,Thought,,0,0,0,,Hiding in plain sight, ain't that right? {?????? lit: fallen leaves among fallen leaves - think he just means "I'll become one of them, indistinguishable"... is it right to use that idiom here?}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.63,0:09:24.56,Thought,,0,0,0,,And in the world of women, \Nyou've gotta be a looker, right? {?????? can't hear but I think he means "all the other girls are pretty, so I have to be pretty too"}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.40,0:09:48.43,Thought,,0,0,0,,Whew... The girls’ section of the school \Nhas these kinds of facilities?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.43,0:09:50.62,Thought,,0,0,0,,This is pure discrimination!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.30,0:09:55.94,Thought,,0,0,0,,How could I ever leave \Nwithout capturing this on film? {????? idk what he means: without focusing on this, what will I do?}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.52,0:10:23.72,Thought,,0,0,0,,Akimoto-sensei!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.07,0:10:26.75,Thought,,0,0,0,,She’s the girls' swimming coach too?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.38,0:10:34.11,Thought,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.54,0:10:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{indistinct}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.16,0:10:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, once you’ve learned the ropes, try it.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.17,0:10:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.43,0:10:59.77,Thought,,0,0,0,,Whoa, can't miss this!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.31,0:11:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You there.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.15,0:11:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sitting it out because of the cold?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.92,0:11:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my! You can’t even speak?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.05,0:11:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You don’t have a fever, though...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.37,0:11:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to the nurse’s office \Nand get some medicine just in case.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.16,0:11:23.55,Thought,,0,0,0,,Whew! That was close.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.55,0:11:25.83,Thought,,0,0,0,,I gotta bail before she figures me out.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.17,0:11:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{Okay, hold it for now!} {yuji thinks she's talking to him (you there, stop!) while she's actually saying it to the girls... idk how to make it sound ambiguous enough} All right, now hold it!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.34,0:11:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That’ll be it for today. \NNow everyone hit the showers.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.38,0:11:35.89,Thought,,0,0,0,,I thought for sure she caught me.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.98,0:11:56.23,Thought,,0,0,0,,Ugh... It was going so well so far! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.00,0:12:02.99,Thought,,0,0,0,,If I go in now, it’ll be the biggest scoop \Nin Jouka's history. I'll be the boys' superhero!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.00,0:12:07.25,Thought,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.80,0:12:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.30,0:12:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You still haven’t gone to the nurse’s office?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.84,0:12:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You’d better hurry and go now.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.09,0:12:34.69,Thought,,0,0,0,,Where on earth is Saori’s classroom?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.69,0:12:39.62,Thought,,0,0,0,,After that declaration, I’ve gotta get solid shots \Nof the 2-C crew, or my infiltration’s pointless.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.62,0:12:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Cut it out!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.35,0:12:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Look at that cute bra you've got! \NLet us see it too! {??? idk what's that burejon}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.83,0:12:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! I said no!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.32,0:12:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, quit struggling! If you don’t behave, \Nwe'll undress you completely!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.63,0:12:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.96,0:12:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what adorable undies! {panty?}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.99,0:12:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.57,0:13:01.83,Thought,,0,0,0,,They've gotta be third-years, for sure. {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.76,0:13:08.98,Thought,,0,0,0,,Oh, crap! The public morals inspector. {dunno what to call her lol but it's not exactly hall monitor}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.19,0:13:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Your tie’s crooked. {to the side}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.09,0:13:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t think I’ve seen you before.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.22,0:13:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a second-year?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.26,0:13:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't wander around the third-year floor for no reason! Go back downstairs.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.80,0:13:36.98,Thought,,0,0,0,,I see! So it's one floor below? {Saori's class }
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.80,0:13:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But does Yuji really have the guts?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.36,0:13:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. He's totally bluffing.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.09,0:13:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So I figured. The next boy caught here won’t just get suspended—he’ll be expelled!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.10,0:13:50.79,Thought,,0,0,0,,Heh! My makeup work is flawless. {genius}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.79,0:13:55.15,Thought,,0,0,0,,Even Saori and the others didn’t bat an eye. \NWhat did I tell you? Don’t come crying later!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.70,0:14:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori, what are you so worried about?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.22,0:14:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.17,0:14:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, even if he {\i1}is{\i0}{\i0\fsp8} {\fsp0}coming, \Nit won’t be so soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.34,0:14:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He gave himself a whole week, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.53,0:14:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.91,0:14:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s no way he’d show up \Non the same day he warned us.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.46,0:14:21.90,Thought,,0,0,0,,You're too naïve, my dear!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.90,0:14:26.02,Thought,,0,0,0,,Don’t you know that infiltration works best \Nby exploiting the enemy’s psychology?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.93,0:14:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I suppose.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.79,0:14:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All the lockers are already in use, \Nand the curtains are all shut tight... {audio drop in the VHS version}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.94,0:14:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s stupid to keep worrying \Nabout every little thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.03,0:14:42.95,Thought,,0,0,0,,Yes, good! \NThat's the spirit!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.85,0:14:52.27,Thought,,0,0,0,,Nobody would suspect that a girl sitting out in PE class is secretly filming them!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.27,0:14:56.83,Thought,,0,0,0,,What's more, Shimizu’s totally got \Na full-on woman’s figure now! {body}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.49,0:15:01.42,Thought,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Kobayashi still looks \Nlike a middle schooler.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.89,0:15:07.65,Thought,,0,0,0,,But in the end, Saori’s got \Nthe cutest body of the bunch!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.30,0:15:13.01,Thought,,0,0,0,,All right, with all three of them together, \Nit's time for a commemorative snapshot.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.30,0:15:22.03,Thought,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.41,0:15:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{Nothing happened, it seems.} Guess I had nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.33,0:15:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.79,0:15:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{If he had that much guts, \NI’d want to show him this myself!} If he really had the guts, \N I'd show him this myself!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.46,0:15:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Manami!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.79,0:15:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I’d give him a real treat too. {big service}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.56,0:15:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.25,0:15:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.72,0:15:44.61,Thought,,0,0,0,,{does this need subs?}{marty: yes, this needs subs.} 1! 2! 3! 4! 5! 6! 7...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.61,0:15:48.81,Thought,,0,0,0,,Now, look here! \NThat's way too bold!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.81,0:15:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! Hurry up! \NToday’s the vault test!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.72,0:15:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.83,0:15:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A surprise test?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.87,0:15:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That sucks... {?????????? no clue}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.64,0:16:01.13,Thought,,0,0,0,,Huge success!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.13,0:16:03.32,Thought,,0,0,0,,All thanks to my go-getter attitude. {lit: When I say I’ll do something, I do it, that's the kind of man I am}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.00,0:16:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you to go to the nurse's office?
Comment: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{Nurse's office typesetting looks kinda funky, might wanna fix it up a bit; it's just fucked bc of the anamorphic video}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.34,0:16:23.84,Thought,,0,0,0,,Huh? That was pretty rough, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.32,0:16:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That was pretty reckless, wasn't it,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.33,0:16:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakazaki-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.77,0:16:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.29,0:16:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You can drop the act now.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.15,0:16:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how good your makeup is,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.75,0:16:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you can’t fool a teacher's eye.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.38,0:16:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a vague feeling about it back then.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.03,0:16:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, you look like a girl, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.12,0:16:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That inconspicuous mark of a boy—an Adam’s apple. {lit: secondary sex characteristic}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.33,0:17:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a genius makeup artist can slip up.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.56,0:17:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If it’s come to this, \NI’m ready for suspension.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.82,0:17:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad. I admire your courage.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.07,0:17:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.16,0:17:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You poor boys...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.20,0:17:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Ma’am... {teacher}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.18,0:17:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're that desperate\Nto see a girl’s naked body,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.59,0:17:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll help you as much as you like.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.02,0:17:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what? {???????????? no idea}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.10,0:17:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not at all! That’s not the real reason \Nwhy we sneak into the girls’ building!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.75,0:17:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to pretend anymore. {enduring something out of pride; putting up with it; grinning and bearing it}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.89,0:17:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Ma’am...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.86,0:17:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll teach you gently,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.02,0:17:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,so go on, do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.02,0:18:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll protect the pure boy in you \Nfrom suspension. {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.74,0:18:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There—what you boys yearn for the most \Nis this garden of flowers. {lit: want to know}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.07,0:18:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{?}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.94,0:18:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re trembling.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.88,0:18:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, right here.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.28,0:18:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{?? maybe  mucha = impossible/no way}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.24,0:18:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Protecting our pure boys \Nfrom suspension is our duty as teachers!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.92,0:18:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn’t tell on you for sneaking in, so please... {infiltrating}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.81,0:18:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Boobs! Boobs! Ah, boobies!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.21,0:18:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... N-No, ma'am, please, h-have mercy... {idk what he means}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.15,0:18:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Bear with it. Not yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.45,0:18:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.93,0:19:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I'm not the only one \N getting excited. You're stiff as a rock.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.42,0:19:08.13,Top,,0,0,0,,7,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.46,0:19:09.27,Top,,0,0,0,,6,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.76,0:19:10.25,Top,,0,0,0,,5,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.84,0:19:11.80,Top,,0,0,0,,4,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.80,0:19:12.59,Top,,0,0,0,,3,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.01,0:19:13.47,Top,,0,0,0,,2,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.14,0:19:14.67,Top,,0,0,0,,1,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.30,0:19:16.21,Top,,0,0,0,,start! {??? idk}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.57,0:19:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.42,0:19:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-The film...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.61,0:19:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stain... A stain! But that's... {?????? maybe "I gotta wash it out" or "sorry", maybe he borrowed that skirt from saori or something}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.70,0:19:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori-chan, goodbye! {again, maybe it's her skirt, could also be just "sore ja"}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.63,0:19:46.96,Thought,,0,0,0,,Yuji’s voice?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.54,0:19:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!\N What am {\i1}I{\i0} supposed to do now?! {maybe "what's wrong with me that he didn't even want to fuck me"}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.10,0:19:57.60,Thought,,0,0,0,,Of course not! {/no way, right}
Dialogue: 4,0:20:11.18,0:20:15.73,Song,,0,0,0,,{BECAUSE by ScooP; got full lyrics from EB's booklet: 見ようともしなかったことに\N君は今瞳を向け始めてる\N「ゴメンネ」とうつむいた君\N僕にはもう信じさせるものがない\N崩れそうなその肩を二度と\N僕は抱けない\NBecause I miss you, Baby. 離れて行く\N怖いなんて言葉にはつばを吐いてきた\NBecause I miss you, Baby. 小さくなる\Nあの頃は君の好きなもの すべて好きだったのに\N手に届く限りのもので\N君は今 幸せを創りあげたね\N夢を側に置きたい君\N夢だけはまだ追い続けていたい僕\N君はたぶん僕以外の男に\N抱かれるんだね\N君が思ってるより 僕は強くないさ\N誰も君の代わりできないから\NBecause I miss you, Baby. 振り向かない\N君の笑顔 今僕の瞳駆けめぐる\NBecause I miss you, Baby. もう見えない\N届かない僕の愛も夢もこの声さえも\NBecause I miss you, Baby.\NBecause I miss you, Baby.\N小さくなる\NBecause I miss you, Baby.\Nもう見えない} You're starting to turn your eyes
Dialogue: 4,0:20:16.95,0:20:25.77,Song,,0,0,0,,to something you never even tried to see
Dialogue: 4,0:20:26.51,0:20:31.36,Song,,0,0,0,,"I'm sorry," you said, bowing your head.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:32.10,0:20:41.17,Song,,0,0,0,,And I no longer had anything you could believe in
Dialogue: 4,0:20:42.13,0:20:47.86,Song,,0,0,0,,I can never hold
Dialogue: 4,0:20:48.61,0:20:56.07,Song,,0,0,0,,those shaking shoulders again {crumbling}
Dialogue: 4,0:20:56.07,0:20:59.90,Song,,0,0,0,,Because I miss you, Baby
Dialogue: 4,0:20:59.90,0:21:03.24,Song,,0,0,0,,I won't look back
Dialogue: 4,0:21:03.24,0:21:11.52,Song,,0,0,0,,Your smile is flashing through my eyes now
Dialogue: 4,0:21:11.52,0:21:15.34,Song,,0,0,0,,Because I miss you, Baby
Dialogue: 4,0:21:15.34,0:21:18.61,Song,,0,0,0,,I can't see you anymore
Dialogue: 4,0:21:18.61,0:21:30.43,Song,,0,0,0,,My love, my dreams, and even my voice won't reach you
Dialogue: 4,0:21:26.60,0:21:30.43,Song,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H880049&}Because I miss you, baby
Dialogue: 4,0:21:34.39,0:21:38.28,Song,,0,0,0,,Because I miss you, baby {sounds like an audio drop after this line, but most people skip the ending song so eh}
Dialogue: 4,0:21:38.28,0:21:41.87,Song,,0,0,0,,I'm getting smaller
Dialogue: 4,0:21:41.87,0:21:46.45,Song,,0,0,0,,Because I miss you, baby
Dialogue: 4,0:21:49.58,0:21:53.58,Song,,0,0,0,,Because I miss you, baby
Dialogue: 4,0:21:53.58,0:21:56.95,Song,,0,0,0,,I can't see you anymore
